This topic describes how to check and monitor current VM status in Ops Manager.

For a complete guide to monitoring Pivotal Application Service (PAS), see [Monitoring PAS](https://docs.pivotal.io/application-service/2-7/operating/monitoring/index.html).


## <a id="interface"></a> Monitoring VMs Using the Ops Manager Interface

To view monitoring information:

1. Navigate to the Ops Manager Installation Dashboard.

1. Click any product tile.

1. Select the **Status** tab.

 <%= image_tag("status-tab.png", :alt => "Screenshot of the Pivotal Elastic Runtime Installation Dashboard. The image shows the 'Status' tab selected with two example jobs.") %>

